description: Welcome the Trouper back to season 3. She is here to Kick ass and chew bubble gum, and she is all out of bubble gum. However, the Jester is feisty and really hates losing. You see, she has this huge fan base that gives her shit when she loses. Best way to describe this match? Back and forth, back and forth, back and forth. Who won? Join and see.
title: The Trouper (3-6) The Jester (0-1)
